headline: Breville launches next generation Oracle® espresso machine, the Oracle Dual Boiler
summary: Breville, the global leader in award-winning coffee innovation, will launch the Oracle Dual Boiler, the latest evolution in its premium espresso machine range on August 25th. Designed to deliver ultimate automation and unparalleled performance, this machine caters to coffee enthusiasts who seek the perfect balance between convenience and control. Offering the ability to switch between auto and manual modes, users can enjoy either a fully automated workflow or hands-on espresso crafting.

headline: Diebold Nixdorf Optimizes Global Service Delivery with Oracle
summary: Diebold Nixdorf (NYSE: DBD), a world leader in transforming the way people bank and shop, has selected Oracle Fusion Cloud Service and Oracle Fusion Cloud Field Service, part of Oracle Fusion Cloud Customer Experience (CX), to optimize its global service operations. With AI-powered cloud applications for customer service, Diebold Nixdorf will be able to unify service operations, improve field technician productivity, and enhance customer satisfaction.
